ec2_config.description:
configuration options for the EC2 Instance:
  - instance_type: The instance type for the EC2 Istance.
  - subnet_id: The subnet ID for the EC2 instance.
  - public_ip: Assign a public IP address to the EC2 Instance (default: false).
  - security_groups: A list of security group IDs to apply to EC2 instance.
  - tags: A map of tags to apply to the EC2 Instance

vpc_config.description:
Configuration options for the VPC:
  - cidr_block: the CIDR block for the VPC.
  - enable_dns_hostnames: Enable or disable DNS hostnames for the VPC (default: true)
  - enable_dns_support: Enable or disable DNS support within the VPC (Default: true)
  - availability_zones: A list of availability zones to create a subnets in (optional)
  - vpc_tags: A map of tags to apply to the VPC (optional).
